OL,6,FHis grandparents Michael Ives, 47, and
OL,7,FKerry Ives, 46, deny murdering the
OL,8,Fboy, who died in hospital two days
OL,9,Flater, and his mother Shannon Ives,
OL,10,F28, denies causing or allowing his
OL,11,Fdeath.
OL,13,FGiving evidence on Monday, 7 July,
OL,14,FShannon Ives became visibly upset when
OL,15,Fshe was asked by David Elias KC,
OL,16,Fdefending her father, whether she had
OL,17,Fever hit Ethan.
OL,19,FShe said: "Either a tap on the hand or
OL,20,Fa tap on the bum, that was it."
