OL,7,Fmentioned that she had seen her father
OL,8,Fshake Ethan on the day of his collapse
OL,9,Funtil she was interviewed by police
OL,10,Falmost a year later.
OL,12,FShe said: "I was told about what the
OL,13,Fdoctors had said in their reports."
